Package: FIR 
Type: Package
Title: Simple Functions for Forest Inventory Data in R 
Version: 0.0.1 
Authors@R: c(person("Jeffrey", "Doser", role=c("aut", "cre"), email="jwdoser@ncsu.edu"))
Author: Jeffrey Doser [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Jeffrey Doser <jwdoser@ncsu.edu>
Description: Implements a variety of common calculations and data summarizations needed when working with forest inventory data. The package's objective is to streamline forest inventory data analysis in R for use in undergraduate forest mensuration and/or biometrics classes.  
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
URL: https://github.com/doserjef/FIR/issues
BugReports: https://github.com/doserjef/FIR/issues
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: dplyr, ggplot2, rlang, tidyr, stats
Suggests: testthat
